title: Summer House: Speak Now or Forever Hold Your Loverboy
description: It's finally here... the moment no one's been waiting for... KyManda's wedding! Yes, The Summer House finale brought us an event three years in the failing, and it was as okay as we expected! Plus, Lindsay and Carl admitted their growing meh-ttraction for each other, and Alex did something we remembered. What a way to end the season!
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
